title: IAMX - Kiss + Swallow
description: The domestic release of their debut. Melding elements from early electronic with trip-hop and the sensibilities of synthpop, IAMX has created an unmistakable, original sound. Features two bonus tracks and a video not found on the European release. Like a hybrid between the sexy swagger of Prince and the cool and collected respectability of Roxy Music, IAMX mixes the erotically charged vocals of Chris Corner (Sneaker Pimps) with music that is frantic yet controlled.
